*
BA E 49 2               ESCAPE
BA C CMD900 2801, 49 2  SET CAL MODE
BA C CMD900 2801, 49 2  SET CAL MODE
BA C CMD920, 49 2       ERASE CAL DATA
BA C CMD955, 49 2       RESET INTERNAL OFFSET
BA C CMD960 2, 49 1     USE INTERNAL OFFSET
BA C CMD110 4, 49 1     RAW MODE
BA C CMD120 10000, 49 1 MULT
BA C CMD125 0, 49 1     OFFSET ZERO
BA C CMD126 0, 49 2     POST CALIBRATION OFFSET ZERO
BA C CMD105 32, 49 1    SET TO 32 SAMPLE AVG
BA C CMD420, 49 1       STORE PARAMETERS
BA C CMD300 2, 49 1     OPERATE
*
*
* START CALIBRATION
* -----------------------------------
* 
TC I 2
TC T 23 3	SET TEMP, WAIT WAS
PC I 2		INITIALIZE PRESSURE CONTROLLER
*
PC P 900 3 	SET PRESSURE, WAIT
BA C CMD940 00 01 1, 49 3 STORE PRESSURE AND TEMPERATURE
*
PC P 800 3 	SET PRESSURE, WAIT
BA C CMD940 00 02 0, 49 3
*
PC P 700 3 	SET PRESSURE, WAIT
BA C CMD940 00 03 0, 49 3
*
TC T 26 3 	SET TEMP, WAIT
PC I 2		INITIALIZE PRESSURE CONTROLLER
BA R 49 3   READ BAROS 49, WAIT 5 SEC 
PC S        STOP PRESSURE
TC S		STOP TEMP
*
ST
* -------------------------------------

